# Getting Started with Computers
Kenneth J. Sauer (kjsauer on GitHub)

## Attention and Focus
Promote the one computer-, one screen-, and one window-at-a-time approach for maintaining attention and focus: A small laptop w/ a 12.5" screen is just fine (perhaps even ideal)!

## Note
It is easy to build (construct) a computer. Choosing good parts is more challenging (i.e., compatible, high functioning, and with the required durability, performance, and reliability specifications).

## Safe Mode
Start Lenovo ThinkPad computer in safe mode: Tap F8 during start-up